sequenceDiagram
    participant HN1 as HN1 (Primary)
    participant HP1 as HP1 (Sec)
    participant DN1 as DN1 (Sec)
    
    Note over HN1, DN1: Time 0s: Normal Operation
    
    HN1->>HN1: [CRASH] System Failure
    
    Note over HP1, DN1: Time 0-10s: Detecting Failure
    
    par Election
        HP1->>DN1: Initiate Election
        DN1->>HP1: Vote (Priority 1)
    end
    
    Note over HP1: Time 15s: Elected New PRIMARY
    HP1->>HP1: Become PRIMARY
    
    Note over HN1, DN1: Time 30min: HN1 Restarts
    HN1->>HP1: Sync Data
    
    Note over HN1: Time 32min: Reclaim PRIMARY
    HN1->>HP1: Step down (Priority 2 > 1)
    HP1->>HP1: Become SECONDARY
    HN1->>HN1: Become PRIMARY